    <headline>Polar low, yellow level, Vesteraalbanks, Banks outside Troms and Tromsoeflaket, 01 March 00:00 UTC to 01 March 15:00 UTC.</headline>
    <description>A polar low vil early Monday morning develop by 74 degrees north and 12 degrees east, and is expected to reach West-Finnmark late Monday morning. The low will give west gale force 8 and occasionally severe gale force 9 south of the center. The wind expected to decrease Monday afternoon. </description>
